Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    net.vivialconnect.model.number.Number.buy(String, String, String, Map<String, Object>)
    This method is deprecated. The API discontinued purchasing random numbers using an area code. If you call this method with an area code, it will choose the first number returned by Number.findAvailableNumbersByAreaCode(String). Also, if you provide a phone number and an area code, the phone number will be ignored. To purchase numbers use Number.buy(String, String, Map) instead. Purchases the specified phone number in this area code with a phone number type.
    net.vivialconnect.model.number.Number.buyLocalNumber(String, String, Map<String, Object>)
    This method is deprecated. The API discontinued purchasing random numbers using an area code. Internally this method will look up for an available number in the API and call Number.buyLocalNumber(String, Map) to keep existing functionality. If you provide a phone number and an area code, the phone number will be ignored. To purchase local numbers use Number.buyLocalNumber(String, Map) instead. Purchases the specified phone number in this area code.
